Git is type of VCS(Version control System) or SCM(Source code managament) tool.
Git is distrubted version control System.it is design to handle minor to major project with high speed and efficiency.
Features of git->
->Open source 
->Speed
->Scalability
->Security

Branching and Merging are the great features of git which make it diffrent from other SCM tools.
Commands on git-
git init ( A hidden file of git has been created)
git status ( it shows untracked files ) (red colour)
git add filename
// it will commit changes 
git status( green color)
git commit -m  message
git log (it will tell us what all commit made till now)
git remote add origin (link )
git push origin master ( file will be added to the github)
